1. bcyptjs:- encrypts passwords , Library
2. config:- global variable declaration , Library
3. jsonwebtoken:- JWT, create authorisation for continous stream to multiple feeds aur links
4. mongoose :- Library, database handling
5. axios:- Library, help to fetch resources from backend in form of http request
6. nodemon :- Start the server
7. concurrently:- can run backend and frontend on same prompt
8. GIT PUSH - git add . && git commit -m "Comments" && git push

Note:-"dependencies" : Packages required by your application in production. "devDependencies" : Packages that are only needed for local development and testing.
nodemon and concurrently are dev Dependencies

